<figureCitation box="[1237,1337,943,969]" captionStart="FIGURES 2–19" captionStartId="2.[136,243,1952,1974]" captionTargetBox="[201,1404,533,1907]" captionTargetId="figure-178@2.[151,1436,502,1930]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 2–19. LM micrographs. 2–7. Gomphosphenia minima C. Delgado, S. Blanco, L. González-Paz &amp; S.F.P.Almeida sp. nov. 8–15. Planothidium lanceolatum. 16–19. Planothidium frequentissimum. Scale bar = 10 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6820927" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6820927/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="138">Figs 2–7</figureCitation>
